<dialogs:ForkPlusDialogWindow xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
                              xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
                              xmlns:dialogs="clr-namespace:ForkPlus.Avalonia.Dialogs"
                              x:Class="ForkPlus.Avalonia.Dialogs.InteractiveRebaseWindow"
                              Title="Interactive Rebase"
                              Width="780" Height="560"
                              MinWidth="520" MinHeight="360"
                              CanResize="True"
                              WindowStartupLocation="CenterOwner">
    <!--
        Phase 5.6a：Avalonia 版 InteractiveRebaseWindow（spike 骨架版）。
        验证 ListBox + DataTemplate + ComboBox 替代 WPF 自定义 ListView + Adorner 拖拽 + IpcServer 通信。

        对照 WPF 工程 src/ForkPlus/UI/Dialogs/InteractiveRebaseWindow.xaml.cs（919 行）：
          - public partial class InteractiveRebaseWindow : ForkPlusDialogWindow, IDisposable
          - 静态字段：InteractiveRebaseComboBoxItem[] InteractiveRebaseComboBoxItems（8 项：
            Pick/Edit/Reword/Squash/Fixup/Drop/Move Up/Move Down）
          - 字段：
            * GitModule _gitModule
            * LocalBranch _sourceBranch
            * IGitPoint _destination
            * IrAction _initialAction
            * IpcServer _riIpcServer
            * Task _riProcessRunner / Semaphore _finishRiProcessSemaphore
            * ObservableCollection<RevisionEntry> _todoList
            * DelayedAction<string> _refreshRevisionDetails
            * (InteractiveRebaseAction, string)[] _initialTodoList
            * bool _closing / _rebaseProcessRunning / _suppressRewordDialog / _updateInProgress
            * string _response / _todoListPath
            * CheckBox _backupCurrentStateCheckBox
            * RepositoryReferences _references
            * RewordAdorner _adorner
          - 构造函数 (RepositoryUserControl, GitModule, LocalBranch sourceBranch, IGitPoint destination, IrAction initialAction)：
            * UpdateRefsCheckBox.IsChecked = ForkPlusSettings.Default.InteractiveRebase_UpdateRefs
            * _backupCurrentStateCheckBox = new CheckBox（动态加到 Footer.CustomSection）
            * ShowCancelButton = true; SubmitButtonTitle = "Rebase"
            * SourceGitPointView.Value = _sourceBranch
            * DestinationGitPointView.Value = _destination
            * RevisionListView.ItemsSource = _todoList
            * RevisionDetails.Initialize(repositoryUserControl, InteractiveRebase)
            * RevisionListFallbackUserControl.Show() + FallbackMessage = "Loading..."
            * SetStatus(InProgress, "")
            * _refreshRevisionDetails = new DelayedAction<string>(...)
            * _rebaseProcessRunning = true
            * _riProcessRunner = Task.Run 调用 RebaseInteractiveGitCommand().Execute(gitModule, destination)
              成功后 UpdateSubmodulesGitCommand（若有）+ Dispatcher.Async Close(rebaseResult)
            * RefreshCommandPreview()
          - GetCommandPreview: "git rebase -i <destination>"
          - OnClosing: 若 _rebaseProcessRunning 则 e.Cancel=true + StopRebaseInteractiveProcess("cancel")
          - IsTodoListChanged / IrCancelConfirmed (MessageBoxWindow.ShowDialog)
          - StopRebaseInteractiveProcess(response)：_response = response + _finishRiProcessSemaphore.Release()
          - CreateBackupBranch: new CreateNewBranchGitCommand().Execute("backup/...")
          - OnSubmit:
            * SetStatus(InProgress, "Rebasing...")
            * contents = string.Concat(_todoList.Reverse().Select(x => x.AsTodoListString(updateRefs)))
            * File.WriteAllText(_todoListPath, contents)
            * SaveMessageArchiveForTodoList(_todoListPath)（JsonConvert.SerializeObject）
            * ForkPlusSettings.Default.InteractiveRebase_UpdateRefs = updateRefs
            * ForkPlusSettings.Default.InteractiveRebase_CreateBackup = ...
            * if (backup) CreateBackupBranch()
            * StopRebaseInteractiveProcess("start")
          - OnPreviewKeyDown: P/E/R/S/F/D 单键 + Ctrl+Up/Down（修改选中项 Action 或移动）
          - RevisionListView_SizeChanged: UpdateListViewColumnsWidth
          - RevisionListView_SelectionChanged: _refreshRevisionDetails.InvokeWithDelay(sha)
          - RevisionListView_MouseDoubleClick: ShowRewordPopup (Drop/Fixup/Squash 除外)
          - ComboBox_SelectionChanged: 选中 Move Up/Down 时调用 MoveUp/MoveDown，
            选中 Reword 时 ShowRewordPopup，其他设置 Action
          - PerformAction(IrAction): 根据 IrAction 类型（Squash/Fixup/Move/Drop/Reword/Edit）
            修改 _todoList + MoveItemToRow + SelectAndScrollIntoView
          - MoveItemToRow / GetRevisionBySha / GetRowBySha
          - MoveUp / MoveDown (reorder in _todoList)
          - ShowRewordPopup (RewordAdorner + RewordUserControl) + UpdateAdornerMargin + CloseRewordPopup
          - IpcMessageHandler: 解析 "prepareTodoListForRebase <path>" → PrepareTodoListForRebase
            + _finishRiProcessSemaphore.WaitOne(Timeout) + pipeServer.WriteString(_response)
          - PrepareTodoListForRebase: GetRebaseTodoListCommand().Execute(gitModule, todoListPath, _references)
            + _todoList.Clear + Populate RevisionEntry + PerformAction(_initialAction)
          - UpdateTodoList: 重算 GraphType / GroupMessage / CustomMessage 等
          - RevisionListViewItem_Drop: 拖拽重排 _todoList

        Avalonia 版差异（spike 简化策略）：
          1. 构造函数重写：解耦 RepositoryUserControl，改为
             (GitModule, string upstreamRef, string? ontoRef, Action? onCompleted)
             * 不再依赖 RepositoryUserControl / LocalBranch sourceBranch / IGitPoint destination / IrAction
             * upstreamRef/ontoRef 用 string 表达（spike 不依赖 IGitPoint 转换）
             * onCompleted 回调替代 Close(GitCommandResult) 退出协议
          2. spike 版用 ListBox + DataTemplate 显示 commit 列表（替代 WPF MultiselectionListView + GridView）
             * 每个 item 一个 ComboBox 选择 action + TextBlock 显示 message + 颜色标识 Border
             * 内部定义 IrAction 枚举（Pick/Reword/Squash/Fixup/Edit/Drop/Skip）
             * 内部定义 InteractiveRebaseItemViewModel 类（Sha/Message/Action/IsEditable）
          3. 拖拽重排 spike 版省略（保留注释说明）
             * WPF 版 RevisionListViewItem_Drop + MoveUp/MoveDown + Adorner 拖拽视觉反馈
             * spike 版不实现 DragDrop.DropEvent + Adorner
          4. IpcServer 通信 spike 版省略（保留注释说明）
             * WPF 版用 IpcServer 等 git rebase -i 调起外部编辑器（RIHelperFilename）后回填 todo list
             * spike 版 OnSubmit 直接构造 rebase 命令序列（不通过 IpcServer）
          5. spike 版省略 OnPreviewKeyDown 单键 + Ctrl+Up/Down（无 Keyboard.IsKeyDown 等价 API）
          6. spike 版省略 ShowRewordPopup（RewordAdorner + RewordUserControl，Adorner 在 Avalonia 11 不可用）
             * Reword action 仍可选，但不弹窗编辑 message
          7. spike 版省略 UpdateRefsCheckBox + _backupCurrentStateCheckBox（不动态加到 Footer.CustomSection）
          8. spike 版省略 GetCommandPreview / RefreshCommandPreview（spike 用 StatusTextBlock 显示）
          9. spike 版省略 RevisionDetails / RevisionListFallbackUserControl（不显示 commit diff 详情）
         10. spike 版省略 CreateBackupBranch + SaveMessageArchiveForTodoList（不写 fork-message-archive）
         11. spike 版省略 Dispose (IpcServer.Dispose)
         12. OnSubmit 直接调用 InteractiveRebaseGitCommand（若存在且 API 匹配）
             * 若 InteractiveRebaseGitCommand 不存在或 API 不匹配（实际只有 RebaseInteractiveGitCommand
               且签名 Execute(GitModule, IGitPoint) 不匹配 spike 的 (gitModule, upstreamRef, ontoRef, todoFile, monitor)）
             * 则 spike 版直接调用 onCompleted?.Invoke() 并 Close

        本 spike 版暂不迁移（留 Phase 5.6b 或更后）：
          - 自定义 MultiselectionListView + GridView（spike 用 ListBox + DataTemplate）
          - 拖拽重排（RevisionListViewItem_Drop + MoveUp/MoveDown + Adorner）
          - IpcServer 通信（_riIpcServer + _finishRiProcessSemaphore + IpcMessageHandler）
          - RewordAdorner + RewordUserControl 双击编辑 commit message
          - OnPreviewKeyDown 单键 P/E/R/S/F/D + Ctrl+Up/Down 快捷键
          - UpdateRefsCheckBox / _backupCurrentStateCheckBox（不动态加到 Footer.CustomSection）
          - GetCommandPreview / RefreshCommandPreview（命令预览）
          - RevisionDetailsUserControl commit diff 详情
          - CreateBackupBranch + SaveMessageArchiveForTodoList
          - RebaseInteractiveGitCommand 真实调用（需 IpcServer 配合）
          - NotificationCenter.ApplicationThemeChanged 主题切换订阅

        本 spike 版验证：
          - ListBox + DataTemplate + ComboBox 渲染 commit 列表正常
          - IrAction 枚举（Pick/Reword/Squash/Fixup/Edit/Drop/Skip）选择切换正常
          - 颜色标识 Border 按 Action 类型着色
          - OnSubmit 回调链路工作（onCompleted?.Invoke + Close）
          - spike 版不实际执行 git rebase -i（依赖 IpcServer + RebaseInteractiveGitCommand，
            spike 简化为仅 UI 验证 + 回调通知）
    -->
    <Grid RowDefinitions="Auto,Auto,*,Auto" Margin="12">
        <!-- Row 0: Header -->
        <TextBlock Grid.Row="0"
                   Name="TitleTextBlock"
                   FontSize="14" FontWeight="Medium"
                   Margin="0,0,0,4" />
        <!-- Row 1: Description -->
        <TextBlock Grid.Row="1"
                   Name="DescriptionTextBlock"
                   FontSize="12"
                   TextWrapping="Wrap"
                   Foreground="{DynamicResource ThemeForegroundLowBrush}"
                   Margin="0,0,0,8" />

        <!-- Row 2: Content -->
        <Grid Grid.Row="2" Margin="0,4,0,0">
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
                <RowDefinition Height="*" />
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <!-- 上游 / 目标 ref 信息（对照 WPF SourceGitPointView + DestinationGitPointView） -->
            <Grid Grid.Row="0" ColumnDefinitions="Auto,*,Auto,*" Margin="0,0,0,8">
                <TextBlock Grid.Column="0"
                           Text="Upstream:"
                           FontSize="12"
                           VerticalAlignment="Center"
                           Margin="0,0,6,0" />
                <TextBlock Grid.Column="1"
                           Name="UpstreamRefTextBlock"
                           FontSize="12"
                           VerticalAlignment="Center"
                           TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"
                           Foreground="{DynamicResource LabelBrush}" />
                <TextBlock Grid.Column="2"
                           Text="Onto:"
                           FontSize="12"
                           VerticalAlignment="Center"
                           Margin="12,0,6,0" />
                <TextBlock Grid.Column="3"
                           Name="OntoRefTextBlock"
                           FontSize="12"
                           VerticalAlignment="Center"
                           TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"
                           Foreground="{DynamicResource LabelBrush}" />
            </Grid>

            <!-- commit 列表（spike 版 ListBox + DataTemplate，对照 WPF MultiselectionListView + GridView） -->
            <Border Grid.Row="1"
                    BorderBrush="{DynamicResource ThemeBorderMidBrush}"
                    BorderThickness="1"
                    CornerRadius="4">
                <ListBox Name="CommitListBox"
                         Background="Transparent"
                         BorderThickness="0">
                    <ListBox.ItemTemplate>
                        <DataTemplate>
                            <Grid ColumnDefinitions="6,140,*" Margin="0,2">
                                <!-- 颜色标识（按 Action 类型着色） -->
                                <Border Grid.Column="0"
                                        Width="4"
                                        Background="{Binding ActionBrush}"
                                        CornerRadius="2" />
                                <!-- ComboBox 选择 action（spike 版用枚举绑定） -->
                                <ComboBox Grid.Column="1"
                                          Name="ActionComboBox"
                                          Margin="6,0,6,0"
                                          ItemsSource="{Binding AvailableActions}"
                                          SelectedItem="{Binding Action, Mode=TwoWay}"
                                          HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                          IsEnabled="{Binding IsEditable}" />
                                <!-- commit message + sha -->
                                <StackPanel Grid.Column="2">
                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Message}"
                                               FontSize="12"
                                               TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"
                                               Foreground="{DynamicResource LabelBrush}" />
                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding ShaShort}"
                                               FontSize="10"
                                               FontFamily="Consolas"
                                               Foreground="{DynamicResource SecondaryLabelBrush}" />
                                </StackPanel>
                            </Grid>
                        </DataTemplate>
                    </ListBox.ItemTemplate>
                </ListBox>
            </Border>
        </Grid>

        <!-- Row 3: Footer -->
        <dialogs:ForkPlusDialogFooter Grid.Row="3" Name="Footer" />
    </Grid>
</dialogs:ForkPlusDialogWindow>
